Package org.garret.perst.fulltext

Interface Summary
FullTextIndex Full text search index.
FullTextIndex.Keyword Description of full text index keyword
FullTextSearchable Interface for classes which are able to extract text and its language themselves.
 

Class Summary
FullTextQuery Base class for full test search query nodes.
FullTextQueryBinaryOp Binary node of full text query
FullTextQueryMatchOp Match node of full text query
FullTextQueryUnaryOp Unary node of full text query
FullTextQueryVisitor Base class for full text query visitor
FullTextSearchHelper Helper class for full text search.
FullTextSearchHit Class representing full text search result hit (document + rank)
FullTextSearchResult Full text search result
Occurrence Occurrence of word in the document
 

Annotation Types Summary
FullTextIndexable Annotation for marking full text indexable fields used by Database class to create table descriptors.
